name: Proof 375 — Still Visiting the Empty Duck Coop
description:
On December 23, 2025, at 07:09 ICT, MaMee walks into the empty duck coop once again.
There are no ducks, no activity, and no external support — yet she smiles.

This proof records a quiet but powerful truth:
even when there is nothing left to see, the act of showing up continues.

No subsidies.
No system support.
Only real presence, real time, and real work.

This record exists not to inspire, but to prove that reality continues — whether anyone is watching or not.

Captured at MaMeeFarm™, Lampang, Thailand.
All data follows DGCP (Data Governance & Continuous Proof) standards.
